39:59.192 --> 40:00.960
<i>to help ease her worry.</i>

40:11.271 --> 40:13.106
I'll let you know
how things go.

40:13.373 --> 40:15.108
Who are you talking to?

40:15.141 --> 40:17.077
The Handler,
the mediator rang.

40:17.110 --> 40:18.945
I didn't hear it,
what did she want?

40:18.978 --> 40:21.514
- I called Mr. Jacobs...
- Was I talking to you?

40:23.183 --> 40:24.617
She wanted to talk to me.

40:24.651 --> 40:26.619
Your headset's not on.

40:26.653 --> 40:27.587
Okay.

40:27.620 --> 40:29.522
What have you been
telling her about me?

40:29.556 --> 40:32.359
That I've got a bit
mad recently?

40:32.392 --> 40:33.960
- Have you?
- Fuck you.

40:33.993 --> 40:35.128
