that idea?

40:38.965 --> 40:40.467
Eve, come on.

40:49.976 --> 40:50.977
Let me explain.

40:51.010 --> 40:52.011
<i>We're trying to help.</i>

40:52.045 --> 40:53.912
<i>You've been missing
your daily check-ins.</i>

40:53.947 --> 40:55.515
