42:11.624 --> 42:13.059
Tom!

42:13.092 --> 42:14.594
<i>What's wrong?</i>

42:15.295 --> 42:16.596
Oh my God.

42:16.629 --> 42:18.231
Hey, are you okay?

42:21.568 --> 42:23.503
