about our options.

43:08.615 --> 43:10.617
Options?

43:13.820 --> 43:15.722
There are no options.

43:16.756 --> 43:18.691
Experiment or not,
that's my child,

43:18.725 --> 43:21.494
that's our child.

43:21.528 --> 43:24.330
What kind of
a mother are you?

43:24.364 --> 43:26.466
What? Seriously...

43:27.834 --> 43:31.504
We're given the opportunity
of a lifetime.

43:31.538 --> 43:35.241
And you choose now to have
a fucking mental breakdown?

43:35.275 --> 43:36.276
I'm not crazy.

43:36.309 --> 43:39.479
Now, it's almost
Christmas Day.

43:39.512 --> 43:41.281
