prepartum depression shit

43:46.753 --> 43:49.322
together for six more days?

43:51.190 --> 43:54.727
Okay Tom,
whatever you say.

43:58.765 --> 44:00.433
God.

44:03.269 --> 44:05.204
<i>Mrs. Jacobs...</i>

44:08.775 --> 44:10.577
