46:45.999 --> 46:48.568
Because I love you,
Mrs. Jacobs.

46:48.601 --> 46:50.536
You don't have to say that.

46:51.404 --> 46:53.306
- Say what?
- "Mrs. Jacobs."

46:53.339 --> 46:56.776
Don't confuse me even more,
I'm delusional enough.

46:58.911 --> 47:00.713
