your marriage.</i>

47:36.582 --> 47:37.884
No, we are not married,
okay.

47:37.917 --> 47:39.585
I don't know what
this experiment is

47:39.619 --> 47:41.821
but I'm six fucking
months pregnant...

47:41.854 --> 47:43.456
<i>Eve.</i>

47:44.457 --> 47:45.892
<i>He's playing you.</i>

49:23.856 --> 49:25.892
Tom, honey?

49:27.194 --> 49:28.728
Just a sec.

49:29.495 --> 49:30.998
I can wait.

49:31.597 --> 49:33.033
