59:19.552 --> 59:21.020
Eve!

59:32.532 --> 59:33.299
Eve!

59:42.809 --> 59:44.511
Go on, say it.

59:44.544 --> 59:46.779
You're not my husband.

59:46.813 --> 59:48.748
Look at me.

59:48.781 --> 59:52.352
